data.title: Oracle Excellence Awards: Specialized Partner of the Year
data.meta_description: Oracle is pleased to recognize award winners in a diverse set of categories representing customers and partners from small and medium businesses to the largest enterprises across all industries. Nominate here: https://www.oracle.com/corporate/awards/nominations.html
data.text:
Oracle is pleased to recognize award winners in a diverse set of categories representing customers and partners from small and medium businesses to the largest enterprises across all industries. Learn more about each award category.

Oracle Excellence Award: Specialized Partner of the Year

This award recognizes Oracle Partner Network Specialized partners who have displayed a commitment to delivering innovative solutions and business achievements, and celebrates partner excellence in sales, marketing, solution development, and customer satisfaction.

Specialized Partner of the Year awards are managed regionally. For additional information, please click here.
